FBIS3-29968 "dreas037_m_94008" FBIS-EAS-94-037 Document Type:Daily Report 24 Feb 1994 Thailand NSC Bans SRV Culture Show in Northeast BK2402070494 Bangkok SIAM RAT in Thai 24 Feb 94 p 16 BK2402070494 Bangkok SIAM RAT Language: Thai Article Type:BFN [Text] The National Security Council [NSC] has decided to ban a request by the Vietnamese to present a cultural exhibition in the northeastern region. It also set stringent measures for dealing with hundreds of thousands of illegal foreign workers. The NSC reasoned that Thailand and Vietnam do not have a cultural exchange agreement and felt that a cultural performance should be staged in the capital.
